It's a build set of ffmpeg and related libraries.

=================================================

For Android Build:
We use standalone toolchain here to build Android libraries.

Method to generate standalone toolchain:
Execute $NDK/build/tools/make-standalone-toolchain.sh --platform=android-8 --install-dir=/Users/yourname/android-toolchain
and it will generate android-toolchain folder in the specifed path, some basic libs and include files are included in the sysroot folder of android-toolchain.
Note:	$NDK is where the android ndk toolkit is installed. 
	The parameter --platform specify the android platform api you want to use.
